(465, 119, 2, '2017-03-16', 'In season 2, while the bloody struggle between Saxons and Vikings engulfs the land, Uhtred sets out to avenge his slain family and reclaim his ancestral home.', 'the-last-kingdom-63333_2.jpg', 77334, '2020-11-27 11:50:10', NULL),
