(718, 174, 2, '2016-04-06', 'Still haunted by the case involving the murder of 11-year-old Danny Latimer, DI Alec Hardy and DS Ellie Miller pick themselves up and continue their investigative work, all the while dealing with the far-reaching consequences of the earlier case.', 'broadchurch-1427_2.jpg', 63912, '2020-11-27 11:51:52', NULL),
(719, 174, 3, '2017-02-27', 'Series 3, the final series, starts three years on from the last series, five years on from the start with a bold new crime story which forces us to ask whether the town has a crack running through it caused by Danny Latimer’s death; is this new crime somehow the long-term legacy of that dark moment?', 'broadchurch-1427_3.jpg', 67851, '2020-11-27 11:51:52', NULL),
