(831, 202, 1, '2011-10-05', 'When the Harmon family relocates to a stately mansion in Los Angeles, disturbing secrets start enveloping each of their lives. As they slowly learn about the mysterious and deadly history of their new house, psychiatrist Ben, Vivien and their teenage daughter Violet find themselves surrounded by all manner of menacing spirits, living and dead.', 'american-horror-story-1413_1.jpg', 3700, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(832, 202, 2, '2012-10-17', 'From Nazis and serial killers, to mutants and aliens, no one is safe inside the walls of the Briarcliff Mental Institution. In a house of healing that’s anything but, troubled nun Sister Jude rules with an iron fist and Dr Arden conducts strange experiments on the facility’s patients.', 'american-horror-story-1413_2.jpg', 3702, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(833, 202, 3, '2013-10-09', 'The few remaining Salem descendants are under assault by forces of ignorance and hate. The young witches seek refuge at Miss Robichaux\'s Academy in New Orleans, including new arrival, Zoe, who harbors a terrifying secret of her own. Fiona, a Supreme Witch with unimaginable powers, is determined to protect the Coven, but her obsessive quest for immortality will lead her to cross paths with a voodoo queen and a murderous slave owner cursed with eternal life.', 'american-horror-story-1413_3.jpg', 3703, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(834, 202, 4, '2014-10-08', 'In 1952, in the quiet, sleepy hamlet of Jupiter, Florida, a troupe of human \"curiosities\" has just arrived to town, coinciding with the strange emergence of a dark entity that savagely threatens the lives of townsfolk and freaks alike.', 'american-horror-story-1413_4.jpg', 62526, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(835, 202, 5, '2015-10-07', 'Homicide detective John Lowe traces a series of grisly murders back to the stylish Hotel Cortez in Downtown Los Angeles and its infamous residents.', 'american-horror-story-1413_5.jpg', 69193, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(836, 202, 6, '2016-09-14', 'After a disturbing incident, a young couple move into a seemingly perfect home built in the 18th century. However, the building\'s close proximity to the site of the Lost Colony\'s disappearance and with horrific events happening at the house the couple start to sense something dark underneath the facade.', 'american-horror-story-1413_6.jpg', 78479, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(837, 202, 7, '2017-09-05', 'Set just after the 2016 U.S. presidential election, the seventh installment follows a community torn apart by a dangerous cult leader who uses fear as a weapon.', 'american-horror-story-1413_7.jpg', 90503, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(838, 202, 8, '2018-09-12', 'Worlds collide as Murder House and Coven come together for season 8.', 'american-horror-story-1413_8.jpg', 106028, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
(839, 202, 9, '2019-09-18', 'In the summer of 1984, five friends escape Los Angeles to work as counselors at Camp Redwood. As they adjust to their new jobs, they quickly learn that the only thing scarier than campfire tales is the past coming to haunt you.', 'american-horror-story-1413_9.jpg', 126646, '2020-11-27 11:52:49', NULL),
