(1017, 245, 1, '2009-09-17', 'The first season of the television comedy series Community originally aired from September 17, 2009 on NBC to May 20, 2010 in the United States. The first three episodes aired at 9:30 pm ET before being moved to 8:00 pm ET. The show was picked up for 22 episodes in October 2009, and an additional 3 episodes were ordered later.\n\nThe show focuses on disbarred lawyer Jeff Winger, and his attempt to get a bachelor\'s degree at a community college. He forms a study group in which they study Spanish.', 'community-18347_1.jpg', 29009, '2020-11-27 11:54:28', NULL),
